### Frontend Components

#### [MODIFY] [src/pages/UploadPage.tsx](file:///f:/C%20drive%20data/squintscale/src/pages/UploadPage.tsx)
- Refactor how the page monitors state after an upload. Currently, it waits for `startAnalysis` (which in `useAnalysis` likely blocks entirely or waits synchronously). 
- Modify `useAnalysis` / [UploadPage](file:///f:/C%20drive%20data/squintscale/src/pages/UploadPage.tsx#38-281) to start a `setInterval` running every 2 seconds hitting the new `GET /api/v1/analyses/{analysis_id}/status` endpoint.
- Add lifecycle hooks to clear the interval upon unmount or transition.
- When polling sees `completed`, navigate the user forcefully to `/results/{analysis_id}`.
- When polling sees `failed`, render the error visibly instead of getting stuck loading.
